<p t="451" d="3036" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​&quot;Sister Shiori, I have a​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​confession to make.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="4121" d="4071" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Three days ago, on my way​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​home from work at 11 PM...&quot;​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="8192" d="1001" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Well, it&#39;s no longer three days ago.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="9193" d="2569" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I got these confessions from like​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​a week ago or something.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="11762" d="2402" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​&quot;I was so exhausted from overtime,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="14565" d="3470" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​that I took an empty​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​priority seat on the train.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="18435" d="3704" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​&quot;I know I shouldn&#39;t have done so​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​as a fully capable healthy adult,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="22973" d="1635" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​but the train was almost empty.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="24608" d="2236" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​&quot;And that night, I just​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​couldn&#39;t stand anymore.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="27311" d="2035" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​&quot;I kept looking around feeling guilty,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="29346" d="2169" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​but no one seemed to​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​need it at that moment.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="31749" d="2168" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​&quot;Still, I feel bad about it, Sister.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="33917" d="1402" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​&quot;Please forgive me for my selfishness.&quot;​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="35586" d="667" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​FORGIVEN!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="36253" d="1368" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I&#39;ve done it too, let&#39;s gooo!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="37621" d="1368" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Wheeee!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="39223" d="1368" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I&#39;ve done it too.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="40758" d="2769" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​But, unlike you, there​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​were people around.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="44261" d="2603" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​But, you see, I don&#39;t think​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​anyone needed it at the time.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="46864" d="1902" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​If I saw a pregnant​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​lady or an old woman,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="48766" d="1801" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​yes, I would give them my seat.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="50567" d="2570" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I have done so, because I felt bad.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="53137" d="2002" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​But if there&#39;s no one​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​around, I&#39;mma take it.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="55639" d="3537" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Because Sister Shiori believes in equality.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="60210" d="1869" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I believe in equality.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="62079" d="2336" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I believe in first come, first serve.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="65282" d="2970" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​If someone desperately needs it,​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​yes, of course, we&#39;ll give it.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="68452" d="3403" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I think that you are too pure​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​and I need to corrupt you.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="72823" d="3403" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I need to make it so you never​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​feel guilt about it again.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
